high_descs: Turn around and walk to the microwave on the black counter on your left.
Grab the knife on the black counter.
Turn left, walk to the wall, make a right, and walk to the green trash bin.
Place the knife in the deep, copper pan that's on the stove.
Grab the deep, copper pan on the stove.
Turn around, walk to the fridge, turn left, and walk to the sink.
Place the copper pan on the corner of the black counter top to the right of the sink.

Turn right and head towards the door.  Turn right and face the stove.
Put the knife in the pan on the left front of the stove.
Grab the pan that is on the left front of the stove.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Put the pan in to the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, walk towards fridge, turn left.
Walk towards sink, turn right.
Grab sink near dishwasher.
